hellip;, a_n)$ 和 $\mathbf{B} = (b_1, b_2, &amp;hellip;, b_n)$，它们之间的欧氏距离 $d$ 可以表示为： $$d(\mathbf{A}, \mathbf{B})</description></item><item><title/><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/TensorFlow/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/TensorFlow/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E6%A0%91/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/%E5%86%B3%E7%AD%96%E6%A0%91/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/%E5%8F%8D%E5%90%91%E4%BC%A0%E6%92%AD%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yindongliang.com/docs/Algorithms/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/%E5%8F%8D%E5%90%91%E4%BC%A0%E6%92%AD%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>